title: Rob Gronkowski retires, Cam Newton's curious plan (Football 3/25)
description:
Will Brinson, Ryan Wilson and John Breech talk about the legacy of Rob Gronkowski after the tight end retired, what the Patriots will do without him on the field moving forward and touched on the rest of the news from around the NFL.
